brokerageName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay
description: Highly sought after City Point location with 2 beds, 2 baths, 2 heated garage parking spaces, enormous 750sqft+ patio, and extra deeded storage in a professionally managed, pet friendly, elevator building. Open kitchen/living space w/ gas fireplace and custom built-ins, a primary suite, central AC, in-unit laundry, built-in sonos speakers, hardwood floors and one of the biggest private patios you'll ever see. Top of the line kitchen w/ Sub-Zero fridge, Wolf 6 burner stove, JennAir drawer microwave, commercial grade hood, quartz countertops, marble backsplash and breakfast bar. Oversized primary suite easily fits a king bed, has a big walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom w/ marble steam shower, soaking tub, and double vanity. Second bed is big and bright. Second bath has a marble shower and laundry. Expansive, professionally landscaped patio is perfect for entertaining w/ a gas line for a grill and electricity for an outdoor TV!  Just steps to the beach, Castle Island and Seaport.
